7 An Act relating to agriculture; creating Kenny’s Law;
defining terms; requiring gates to remain closed at
8 all times; allowing for certain exceptions;
prescribing penalties for violation; authorizing the
9 promulgation of rules; providing statement of intent;
providing for noncodification; providing for
